-- Prudential Adds Wells Fargo Bankers in Apartment Push
-- B y   S u s a n n a   P a k
-- 2012-09-13T15:06:34Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-09-13/prudential-adds-wells-fargo-bankers-in-commercial-mortgage-bet.html
Prudential Financial Inc. (PRU) , the
second-largest U.S. life insurer, hired Patrick McAllister and
Laurie Morfin from  Wells Fargo & Co. (WFC)  to bolster the unit making
loans for multi-family dwellings.  McAllister will work in San Francisco and Morfin in a new
Carlsbad, California, office, according to a Business Wire
statement today from Newark, New Jersey-based Prudential.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Susanna Pak in New York at 
 spak10@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Dan Kraut at   dkraut2@bloomberg.net  